        <text x="295" y="135" fill="#5a5a56" font-family="'DM Sans',sans-serif" font-size="13">Área 1 ha (10.000 m²):</text>
        <text x="295" y="155" fill="#0F6E56" font-family="'DM Sans',sans-serif" font-size="18" font-weight="500">N = 400 píxeles</text>
