        <text x="287" y="100" text-anchor="middle" fill="#9a9a94" font-family="'DM Sans',sans-serif" font-size="20">→</text>
        <text x="287" y="118" text-anchor="middle" fill="#9a9a94" font-family="'DM Sans',sans-serif" font-size="11">reproyecta</text>
